§ T11-W6+ § specs/grand-vision/21_SELF_PUBLISH_APOCKY_COM.csl
§§ Self-publish via apocky.com · Vercel-hosted · NO Steam/itch/Epic
§§ Apocky 2026-05-01 directive : "We self publish and host our own download webpage through Vercel at Apocky.com"
§§ status @ ◐ design-pending · enforcement @ wave-9
§§ AMENDS spec/17 § DISTRIBUTION-CHANNELS · TIER-B distribution-channel UPDATED

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ AXIOMS (¬ negotiable · t∞)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

A-1 : self-publish via-apocky.com · Vercel-hosted · NO third-party-storefront-cuts (¬ Steam-30% · ¬ Epic-12% · ¬ itch-10%)
A-2 : Apocky owns-the-distribution-pipeline end-to-end (domain · CDN · payment · entitlement · delivery · update)
A-3 : Stripe = ONLY-payment-processor · 2.9% + $0.30/transaction (industry-standard · ¬ 30%-storefront-cut)
A-4 : binary-integrity via Ed25519-signing + BLAKE3-content-hashing (replaces Steam-DRM · already-designed in-substrate)
A-5 : auto-update via cssl-host-hotfix-stream (already-W8-target) · binary-deltas served-via-Vercel-Pro-Storage-or-Cloudflare-R2
A-6 : direct-exe-download for-launch-v1 · optional-launcher-app deferred-to-post-launch
A-7 : NO third-party-DRM · NO anti-cheat-rootkit · NO kernel-driver · sovereign-respecting · player-machine-respected
A-8 : entitlement-server-of-truth = Supabase + Stripe-webhooks · client-validates-against-server on-equip-action

§ thesis : self-publish maximizes-Apocky-revenue + maximizes-player-trust + minimizes-third-party-dependencies · the-mycelial-substrate IS-the-distribution-network · t∞

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ APOCKY.COM SITE-ARCHITECTURE
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ apocky.com (Vercel-Pro · custom-domain) hosts :
  ⊑ MARKETING : landing-page · trailer · feature-tour · screenshots · press-kit
  ⊑ DOWNLOAD : buy-now → Stripe-checkout → entitlement-granted → download-link (signed-URL · short-TTL)
  ⊑ ACCOUNT : login (Supabase Auth · OAuth Google/Apple/Discord/email-magic-link) · profile · purchase-history
  ⊑ TRANSPARENCY : per spec/17+18 · /transparency/{spending,akashic,mycelial-contributions,sovereign-cap,coder-history}
  ⊑ COMMUNITY : devblog · changelog · roadmap (public-subset of-grand-vision specs) · creator-attribution-page (Apocky · Lyra · Savannah)
  ⊑ DOCS : auto-built-from-specs/grand-vision/ · public-subset · for-modders + curious-readers
  ⊑ BAZAAR-LITE : public-stall-listings · browse-only · login-to-purchase-via-game-not-website
  ⊑ AKASHIC-LITE : public-imprint-browse · login-to-imprint-via-game-not-website
  ⊑ HOME-LITE : public-listed-Homes · browse-only · visit-via-game

§ apocky.com domain · DNS @ Vercel-Pro custom-domain
  ⊑ A-record + AAAA-record → Vercel-edge-network
  ⊑ SSL/TLS auto-managed via Vercel · Let's-Encrypt-rotation
  ⊑ subdomain : downloads.apocky.com → Cloudflare-R2 OR-Vercel-Blob (binary-delivery · CDN-cached)
  ⊑ subdomain : api.apocky.com → cssl-edge serverless-functions (Vercel-edge)
  ⊑ subdomain : akashic.apocky.com → public-imprint-browser (Vercel-edge)
  ⊑ subdomain : status.apocky.com → status-page (uptime · scheduled-maintenance · rolled-out-hotfixes)

§ Vercel infrastructure-tier :
  ⊑ Vercel-Pro ($20/month) for-custom-domain + analytics + serverless-function-bandwidth
  ⊑ Vercel-Blob OR Cloudflare-R2 for-binary-storage (game-installer · auto-update-deltas) · ~100GB total · ~$15-30/month at-scale
  ⊑ Vercel-Edge-Config for-feature-flags (gradual-rollout per spec/11 KAN-RIDE A/B-protocol)

§ existing scaffolding-already-built @ cssl-edge
  ⊑ Next.js 14 app-router (already-scaffolded W3b)
  ⊑ Supabase-client wrapper (W5a)
  ⊑ Stripe-checkout routes (planned W8-D1)
  ⊑ marketplace + companion-stream + asset-recommend (W4 · W5c)
  ⊑ transparency dashboard (W6 + W8 expansion)
  ⊑ NEW @ this spec : landing-page · download-page · launcher-update-API · binary-CDN-routing

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ PURCHASE + DOWNLOAD FLOW
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ visitor-flow @ apocky.com
  1 visitor lands @ apocky.com landing-page
  2 clicks "Buy Now" → /buy
  3 /buy redirects-to Stripe-Checkout (server-side · cssl-host-stripe-integration · cap-gated · idempotency-key)
  4 Stripe-Checkout @ stripe.com handles-payment (PCI-DSS-SAQ-A scope-min · NEVER-touch-raw-cards)
  5 Stripe-webhook @ /api/payments/stripe/webhook fires on-success · webhook-signature-verified
  6 webhook handler grants-entitlement @ Supabase entitlements table (player_id · product_id · purchased_at)
  7 player redirected-back-to apocky.com /download
  8 /download issues-signed-URL (short-TTL · Ed25519-signed by-server) → CDN-fetch
  9 CDN serves LoA.exe-installer · client downloads
 10 player-runs-installer · creates Ed25519-keypair LOCALLY · OS-keychain-stored
 11 first-launch · player logs-in via Supabase-Auth · entitlement-verified · play

§ key-design @ entitlement-server-of-truth :
  ⊑ binary-itself unrestricted (anyone can-RUN it · we don't fight-the-binary)
  ⊑ ALL-multiplayer + ALL-cosmetic-equip + ALL-Akashic-imprint REQUIRES login + entitlement-check
  ⊑ pirated-binary can-PLAY single-player · CANNOT access-Bazaar/Mycelial/Akashic/multiplayer/cosmetics
  ⊑ this-is-our-anti-piracy : the-game-without-mycelium is-shallow · the-mycelium-requires-entitlement
  ⊑ ¬ DRM · ¬ rootkit · ¬ kernel-driver · sovereign-respecting

§ refund-flow
  ⊑ /api/payments/stripe/refund-request · player-initiates within-14-days
  ⊑ automated-process via Stripe-API · server-revokes-entitlement · refund-issued
  ⊑ in-game-content (Aetheric-Shards spent · Akashic-imprints made) refundable on-prorata-basis @ 14-day-window
  ⊑ Stabilized-Essence (earned-currency) NOT-refundable (it's-not-purchased)
  ⊑ jurisdictional-compliance : EU 14-day-statutory + UK 14-day · CN 7-day · etc · auto-handled-via Termly-rules

═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
§ AUTO-UPDATE PIPELINE
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ binary-update-flow (extends cssl-host-hotfix-stream W8 target)
  1 game-launch · checks Σ-Chain TIER-3 hotfix-stream for-new-versions
  2 manifest @ apocky.com /api/launcher/manifest returns latest-version · BLAKE3-content-hash · Ed25519-signed-by-Apocky-master-key
  3 client compares-against current-version · IF outdated → fetch-binary-delta from CDN
  4 binary-delta = bsdiff or-similar · 1-10 MB-typical (vs 100+ MB full-binary)
  5 client verifies-Ed25519-signature · applies-delta · re-launches-with-new-version
  6 cssl-host-attestation logs hotfix-applied @ directive-axis "ImplementationTransparency"
  7 player can-roll-back via Mycelial-Terminal in-Home @ 30-second-window OR last-snapshot

§ rollout-cadence (per spec/11 KAN-RIDE A/B + spec/16 hotfix-classes)
  ⊑ HF-1 KAN-WEIGHT : canary-10% · graduate-or-rollback per-spec/11 criteria
  ⊑ HF-2..7 cosmetic/balance/recipe : 25% canary · 24-hour-soak · graduate-to-100% if-no-disagreement-flags
  ⊑ HF-8 RENDER-PARAM : 100% immediate (auto-rollback on FPS-degradation)
  ⊑ HF-6 SECURITY : 100% immediate · sovereign-cap-prompt-required for-policy-changes
  ⊑ ALL-rollouts have player-revoke-button · always-effective · sovereign-respecting

§ launcher-app (DEFERRED to-post-launch · NOT v1)
  ⊑ for-v1 : direct-exe with-self-update built-in · simplest path
  ⊑ post-launch : optional Tauri-or-similar 5-MB-launcher for-richer-UX (profile-mgmt · install-location-mgmt · auto-launch-on-system-startup)
  ⊑ DO NOT-block-launch on-launcher · ship-direct-exe v1 · gather-feedback · build-launcher-if-demanded

