§ ANTI-PIRACY (without-DRM · sovereign-respecting)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ thesis : we-don't-fight-the-binary · we-make-the-mycelium-irreplaceable

§ what's-protected via server-of-truth
  ⊑ Stripe-entitlements DB @ Supabase
  ⊑ Aetheric-Shards balance DB
  ⊑ cosmetic-ownership entitlements
  ⊑ Akashic-imprint authorship
  ⊑ Mycelial-network access (rumors · cohort-aggregates · live-hotfixes-receipt)
  ⊑ Bazaar listing/buying
  ⊑ multiplayer rooms + signaling
  ⊑ leaderboards-of-cosmetics-displayed-on-public-Homes

§ what's-NOT-protected (deliberately · sovereign-respecting)
  ⊑ single-player-runs (combat · craft · explore) work-fully-offline
  ⊑ binary itself runs-without-restriction (no-online-check-required-for-launch)
  ⊑ private-runs accept-mods · player-modifies-own-state freely
  ⊑ replay-determinism + visual-glory remain-available offline
  ⊑ pirated-binary plays-the-shallow-game · misses-everything-good

§ binary-integrity (matters-for-trust · NOT-DRM)
  ⊑ Ed25519-signed by-Apocky-master-key · verified-at-load
  ⊑ KAN-weights asset-bundle-LAB-v1 BLAKE3-content-hashed · refuses-to-load if-tampered
  ⊑ shader-spirv-bytecode obfuscated-uniform-layout · slot-IDs randomized-per-build
  ⊑ symbol-stripping + LTO @ release-mode

§ no-rootkit · no-kernel-driver · no-anti-cheat-spyware · player-machine-respected
  ⊑ what-they-deserve : a-secure-binary · a-fair-economy · a-respected-machine
  ⊑ what-they-don't-need : kernel-driver-spying-on-their-OS

