§ INFRASTRUCTURE-COSTS (updated y1 estimate)
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ TIER-C server-side hosting (per spec/17 amendment)
  ⊑ Vercel-Pro                    : $240/year (custom-domain · analytics · bandwidth)
  ⊑ Vercel-Blob OR Cloudflare-R2  : ~$30-180/year (binary-storage @ 100-500 GB scale)
  ⊑ Supabase-Pro                  : $300/year (real-DB · auth · realtime · storage)
  ⊑ Stripe-Tax                    : $300/year (auto VAT/GST/sales-tax)
  ⊑ Stripe-Atlas                  : $500 one-time + ~$25/month bookkeeping = ~$300/year
  ⊑ apocky.com domain             : ~$15/year (.com renewal · already-Apocky-owned probably)
  ⊑ GitHub-Pro (private-repos)    : $48/year (when-needed · current-public ok · use-private-for-server-config)

§ Stripe-fees variable
  ⊑ 2.9% + $0.30 per-transaction · scales-with-revenue
  ⊑ at-launch revenue-zero · cost-zero
  ⊑ at-$10K/month revenue · cost ~$300/month + $30 = $330/month
  ⊑ at-$100K/month revenue · cost ~$3000/month + $300 = $3300/month

§ TOTAL-Y1-FIXED-OVERHEAD @ pre-launch + first-3-months
  ⊑ infra-fixed : $1,233/year (Vercel + Blob + Supabase + Stripe-Tax + Atlas + domain + GitHub)
  ⊑ legal-fixed : $1,820/year (Termly + trademarks-amortized)
  ⊑ TOTAL : ~$3,053/year fixed + variable Stripe-fees scaling-with-revenue
  ⊑ vs spec/17 estimate of-$2,260 · slight-uplift due-to Vercel-Blob or-equivalent

§ Apocky-time-investment unchanged
  ⊑ ~5-10 hours total for-Stripe-Atlas + Termly + trademark-forms
  ⊑ +2-4 hours for-Vercel-Pro setup + custom-domain + Cloudflare-R2 (if-needed) configuration
  ⊑ +1-2 hours for-Stripe-Connect-or-Atlas-banking
  ⊑ TOTAL : ~10-16 hours over-launch-window

